<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.4.4">
<l>eṉṉīrmai kaṇṭiraṅki yitutakā teṉṉāta</l>
<l>veṉṉīla mukilvaṇṇark keṉcoliyāṉ collukēṉō</l>
<l>naṉṉīrmai yiṉiyavarkaṇ ṭaṅkāteṉ ṟoruvāycco</l>
<l>ṉaṉṉīla makaṉṟilkā ṇalkutirō nalkīrō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What will I speak with words to my man of blue cloud-colour,</l>
<l>who, seeing my state, does not lament [and] say: “this is not right”?</l>
<l>Speak with one mouth, good blue Makaṉṟils: “now the good state will</l>
<l>not stay with her.” Will you grant [that], will you not?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
